      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>For better or worse, people tend to form their opinions of your very quickly</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Cha 15</p><hr /><p><strong>Benefit:</strong> When you interact with someone for the first time whose starting attitude is indifferent or better, you can immediately attempt a @Check[type:diplomacy] to @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.GMkLZsN3a7YPvA03.JournalEntryPage.1tzIBDaDAO4hmX5C#change-attitude]{change their attitude}. You can’t use any other ability that would modify this Diplomacy check. This check does not count against the typical limit on changing a target’s attitude of once (or twice with additional interaction) per 24 hours.</p>"
